In short, I don't know where to write this. And why am I writing this anyway, because I'm not your fan, and I'm not subscribed to you. I wouldn't even know about you if I hadn't come across some video with you a long time ago. But in general, what I want to say is. If you think that your VTuber life is over, then know that it's not a fact. As long as you want to do this, you can find a way to do this.Well, if you still can't continue to be a Vituber, then become a regular YouTuber. Your subscribers and fans will probably be very happy. Of course, it will not be the same you, that is, not Gavr Gurai, but what if you play a slightly different role, but also Gavr Gurai. I mean that, for some reason, you became completely human. I wouldn't even know about you if I hadn't come across some video with you a long time ago. But anyway, what do I want to say? If you think that your life as a VTuber is over, then know that it's not a fact. As long as you want to do it, you find a way to do it. Maybe it's my destiny, like to try to somehow bring you back? To bring you back... Well, I said it. Oh well, good luck to you in your future life, and bye. (I'm giving you part of my luck, and don't think I'm joking.
